data.value: SimPe is a Tool that can be used to change the internal Data of "The Sims 2". Many People have used SimPe without problems. However, if you are not careful this Tool can damage your Game or even your System. Do not use SimPe if you don't want to take that Risk! Remember SimPe is in its alpha Stage! Please make sure you have a working backup copy of "My Documents\EA Games\The Sims 2\" before you start SimPe. Start SimPe now?

data.name: [Description:KeepFilesOpen]
